{
    "id": 213146,
    "title": "Bekendtgørelse om ændring af liste A til lov om foranstaltninger mod smitsomme sygdomme og andre overførbare sygdomme",
    "documentTypeId": "60",
    "isSagsforlobPeriodValid": true,
    "shortName": "BEK nr 156 af 27/02/2020",
    "documentHtml": "<div class=\"bjelke\">Oversigt (indholdsfortegnelse)</div><table class=\"Indholdsfortegnelse\">\r\n   <tr>\r\n      <td class=\"IndholdsfortegnelseId\">\r\n         <a href=\"#idbd53cf19-852f-4974-a446-1a97032c3071\">Bilag 1</a>\r\n      </td>\r\n      <td class=\"IndholdsfortegnelseTekst\">Liste A</td>\r\n   </tr>\r\n</table><div class=\"bjelke\">Den fulde tekst</div><p class=\"Titel2\">Bekendtgørelse om ændring af liste A til lov om foranstaltninger mod smitsomme sygdomme og andre overførbare sygdomme</p>\r\n<p class=\"Indledning2\">I medfør af § 2, stk. 2, i lov om foranstaltninger mod smitsomme sygdomme og andre overførbare sygdomme, jf. lovbekendtgørelse nr. 1026 af 1. oktober 2019, og efter indstilling fra Sundhedsstyrelsen, fastsættes:</p>\r\n<p class=\"Paragraf\" id=\"idfe7122e3-47cf-4e18-ab30-0ebc60065693\">\r\n   <span id=\"P1\">\r\n   </span>\r\n   <span class=\"ParagrafNr\" id=\"Par1\">§ 1.</span> Liste A over alment farlige sygdomme, som angivet i lovens bilag 1, ændres, så Middle East respiratorisk syndrom (MERS) med den internationale betegnelse: Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS), Krim-Congo hæmorrhagisk feber med den internationale betegnelse: Crimean-Congo haemorrhagic fever, Multiresistent tuberkulose (MDR-TB og XDR-TB) med den internationale betegnelse: Multidrug-resistant tuberculosis (MDR-TB &amp; XDR-TB), og Nipah-virus med den internationale betegnelse: Nipah virus optages på listen, som angivet i bilag 1 til denne bekendtgørelse.</p>\r\n<p class=\"Paragraf\" id=\"id7d0ecb19-b921-4b3b-9323-2a5aa8a4310d\">\r\n   <span id=\"P2\">\r\n   </span>\r\n   <span class=\"ParagrafNr\" id=\"Par2\">§ 2.</span> Bekendtgørelsen træder i kraft den 29. februar 2020.</p>\r\n<p class=\"Stk2\">\r\n   <span class=\"StkNr\" id=\"id11498a16-0c0e-4313-89ec-5c70437f0a8d\">Stk. 2.</span> Bekendtgørelse nr. 301 af 24. juni 1985 om liste A til lov om foranstaltninger mod smitsomme sygdomme ophæves.</p><div class=\"Givet\" id=\"Givet\"><p class=\"Givet\" align=\"center\">Sundheds- og Ældreministeriet, den 27. februar 2020</p><p class=\"Sign1\" align=\"center\">Magnus Heunicke</p><p class=\"Sign2\" align=\"right\">/ Michelle Aagaard</p></div><a id=\"idbd53cf19-852f-4974-a446-1a97032c3071\">\r\n   <hr class=\"BilagStreg\" />\r\n</a>\r\n<p class=\"Bilag\">\r\n   <span id=\"B1\">\r\n   </span>\r\n   <span id=\"Bil1\">Bilag 1</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"BilagTekst\">Liste A</p>\r\n<p class=\"KapitelOverskrift2\">Alment farlige sygdomme jf. lovens § 2, stk. 1</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n   <span class=\"Italic\">Sygdomsbetegnelse</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n   <div style=\"width:100%\">\r\n      <table class=\"Containertable\" style=\"border-style: none; border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px; margin: 0.55cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; \">\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border-style: none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">\r\n               <table valign=\"top\" class=\"Maintable\" width=\"659\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\">\r\n                  <colgroup>\r\n                     <col width=\"218px\">\r\n                     </col>\r\n                     <col width=\"276px\">\r\n                     </col>\r\n                  </colgroup>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:17px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Italic\">Dansk</span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Italic\">International</span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:17px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Kopper</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Smallpox</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:16px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Alvorlig coronavirusinfektion (Svær akut respiratorisk syndrom (SARS) og Middle East respiratorisk syndrom (MERS))</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome (SARS), Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS)</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:33px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Viral hæmorhagisk feber (Ebola, Lassa og Marburg) og Krim-Congo hæmorrhagisk feber</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Viral hemorrhagic fevers (Lassa-fever, Ebola viral disease, Marburg viral disease) &amp; Crimean-Congo haemorrhagic fever</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:17px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Pest</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Plague</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:17px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Difteri</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Diphtheria</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:17px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Multiresistent tuberkulose (MDR-TB og XDR-TB)</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Multidrug-resistant tuberculosis (MDR-TB &amp; XDR-TB)</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:17px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Nipah-virus</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.15cm;padding-top:0.15cm;padding-right:0.15cm;padding-bottom:0.1cm;\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Nipah virus</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n               </table>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </div>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>",
